																					POME-MAS&trade; (Palm Oil Mill Effluent Mesophilic Anaerobic Treatment System)</h1>
																			</div>
																		</div>
																		<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-3d5addd elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="3d5addd" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
																			<div class="elementor-widget-container">
