																					<div class="page" title="Page 6">
																						<div class="section">
																							<div class="layoutArea">
																								<div class="column">
																									<p><b>POME-MAS™ was borne through BiON’s in-house R&amp;D capabilities and knowledge of 40 years in mesophilic anaerobic digestion for wastewater treatment. </b></p>
																									<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">POME-MAS™ is designed to provide higher yields of biogas production and greater reduction efficiency in the chemical oxygen demand (COD) of treated POME. </span></p>
																									<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">A higher efficiency in the treated POME’s COD reduction enables greater amounts of biogas to be produced and increased power generation supply to the grid or palm oil mills.</span></p>
																									<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">BiON continuously strives to progress its R&amp;D efforts of innovating new techniques and methodologies to enhance the anaerobic processes in the treatment of POME. </span></p>
